---
title: Nourishing Cannellini Bean & Roast Veggie Salad with Sweet Dijon Dressing & Feta
description: We love cannellini beans because they are protein-rich, filling and satisfying but their flavour might best be described as
earthy, perfect for a veggie salad! To stay on theme, we've added hearty beetroot, cauliflower and potato. Stir through a
sunny dijon dressing to lighten it up and you've got yourself a dinner that’s brimming with goodness.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
